{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072970/extras/Tri_tags_and_panel-02.png?t=1733259750\" /><br><br>Action Roguelite that blends elements of Vampire Survivors with Fantasy RPG themes. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game introduces a unique mechanic where the player controls three heroes instead of one, offering a fresh and strategic gameplay experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring a JRPG-inspired hand-drawn art style and an intriguing storyline. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tri-Survive is set in a fantasy medieval world that features Kingdoms, knights, elves, goblins and fantastical creatures!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One day these nations fall under a sudden attack by mysterious demonic beings from another dimension, and the heroes of these nations must unite to defeat these beings and unravel the mystery behind their sudden emergence! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072970/extras/Tri_tags_and_panel-01.png?t=1733259750\" />\u00a0 \u00a0 <br>Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Tri-Hero Control &amp; Role-Based Synergy: Manage three heroes simultaneously, each with unique abilities tied to their roles as Tank, Healer &amp; DPS. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Hand-Drawn Art style: Visually stunning, Fantasy RPG-inspired hand-drawn graphics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Engaging Storyline: Immerse yourself in a light but captivating narrative that ties the gameplay together.<br> <br>- Dynamic Progression: Unlock new heroes and team compositions as you progress.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072970/extras/Tri_tags_and_panel-03.png?t=1733259750\" /><br><br>Alpha version is coming soon! Join our Discord for free access to the closed testing. Be part of the community and help shape the future of <i>Tri Survive</i>.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">*Join our Discord for exclusive updates and latest news: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072970/extras/About_Section_Banner-02.png?t=1733259750\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072970/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733259750","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072970/page.bg.jpg?t=1733259750","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072970/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733259750","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072970/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733259750","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072970/extras/Tri_tags_and_panel-02.png?t=1733259750\" /><br><br>Action Roguelite that blends elements of Vampire Survivors with Fantasy RPG themes. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game introduces a unique mechanic where the player controls three heroes instead of one, offering a fresh and strategic gameplay experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring a JRPG-inspired hand-drawn art style and an intriguing storyline. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tri-Survive is set in a fantasy medieval world that features Kingdoms, knights, elves, goblins and fantastical creatures!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One day these nat